d that allows a \"hovered\" state.\r\n  -  Replaced the type of element::catalog_data_cell and element::addon_data_cell from Container to TableRow\r\n  - Added custom styling for the new type by following the guideline of the other element in gui/style.rs to show a border around  hovered row \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5583893/100759631-21139b00-33f1-11eb-901d-75a4d8d03d49.png)\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] Tested on Windows\r\n- [x] Tested on MacOS\r\n- [ ] Tested on Linux\r\n- [ ] Added an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` if knowledge of this change could be valuable to users\r\n", "created_at": "2020-12-01T15:22:38Z", "updated_at": "2020-12-07T09:37:08Z", "closed_at": "2020-12-06T14:49:54Z", "merged_at": "2020-12-06T14:49:54Z", "merge_commit_sha": "b5ab26f4875b19fb725e7324f98fd7f6f504aefa", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [{"id": 2469541265, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyNDY5NTQxMjY1", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ajour/ajour/labels/S%20-%20gui", "name": "S - gui", "color": "ffb5a7", "default": false, "description": ""}, {"id": 2469544583, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyNDY5NTQ0NTgz", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ajour/ajour/labels/enhancement", "name": "enhancement", "color": "84b7eb", "default": true, "description": ""}], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ajour/ajour/pulls/403/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ajour/ajour/pulls/403/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ajour/ajour/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ajour/ajour/issues/403/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ajour/ajour/statuses/0cefb7cd36b4f093a4279384f0553b367eae890d", "head": {"label": "kawashita86:feature/highlight-row", "ref": "feature/highlight-row", "sha": "0cefb7cd36b4f093a4279384f0553b367eae890d", "user": {"login": "kawashita86", "id": 5583893, "n